Paul Guidé https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Guid%C3%A9 0 Paul Guidé (March 18, 1884 – October 16, 1940) was a French film actor of the silent era. Guidé appeared in more than sixty films before 1930 including La dame de Monsoreau (1913) in which he played Henry III of France.
